        <item>
            <title>Spotify HiFi 高音质串流或 2025 年推出，多项增值功能</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/02/19/spotify-hifi-music-pro-2025/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=spotify-hifi-music-pro-2025</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/02/19/spotify-hifi-music-pro-2025/fun-tech/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[arthur]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Wed, 19 Feb 2025 01:55:45 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[科技新闻]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[spotify hifi]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1292571</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Spotify 自 2021 年首次宣布计划推出 HiFi 无损音质串流服务后，用家已经苦等多年。根据最新消息，这项名为「Music Pro」的新高阶订阅计划，或将于 2025 年内正式推出。</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">「Music Pro」计划除了提供无损音质串流外，还将加入一系列额外功能，例如歌曲混音、演唱会门票折扣、优先购买权，以及抢先听音乐或参与音乐会问答会等特权。据估计，这项服务的额外收费约为每月 5 至 6 美元（约港币 39 至 47 元），相比 Spotify 现时 Premium 计划（11.99 美元/月）价格更高。</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Spotify 近期为此与 Warner Music Group 和 Universal Music Group 签订多年的授权协议，解决版权问题，同时探索更多超级粉丝专属的服务，如独家欣赏派对和高质版专辑内容等。</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">值得留意的是，目前 Apple Music 和 Amazon Music 已在基本订阅计划中提供无损音质服务，Spotify 则希望透过「Music Pro」的附加功能为用家带来更高价值，并在竞争激烈的音乐串流市场中突围而出。</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">多年来，Spotify 用家对 HiFi 串流的期待从未减退，而在 2025 年，这项高音质体验终于有望成为现实。</span></p><p><b>来源：</b><a href="https://www.theverge.com/news/614091/spotify-music-pro-hifi-streaming-service-release-date-2025"><span style="font-weight: 400;">The Verge</span></a></p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2025/02/19/spotify-hifi-music-pro-2025/fun-tech/">Spotify HiFi 高音质串流或 2025 年推出，多项增值功能</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
            <wfw:commentRss>https://unwire.hk/2025/02/19/spotify-hifi-music-pro-2025/fun-tech/feed/</wfw:commentRss>
            <slash:comments>0</slash:comments>
        </item>
        <item>
            <title>暂列史上最卖座电影第 8 位  《哪吒 2》超越《头脑特工队 2》成全球动画票房冠军</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/02/19/nazha-no1-animation/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=nazha-no1-animation</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/02/19/nazha-no1-animation/fun-tech/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[arthur]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Wed, 19 Feb 2025 01:00:06 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[科技新闻]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[mario]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[哪吒]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[哪吒 2]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[头脑特工队]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1292554</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>《哪吒之魔童闹海》自 2025 年 1 月 29 日于中国内地上映以来，全球票房已突破 16.98 亿美元（约港币 132.44 亿元），超越《头脑特工队 2》，跃居全球动画电影票房榜首。灯塔专业版数据显示，该片票房仍持续增长，最终票房预测超过 150 亿人民币（约港币 162 亿元），成为全球动画电影史上新霸主。</p><p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1292560" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250218221850-694x395.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="395" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250218221850-694x395.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250218221850.jpg 924w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>由导演饺子执导的《哪吒之魔童闹海》（下称:哪吒 2）延续前作世界观，讲述哪吒与敖丙历经天劫后灵魂虽存，但即将魂飞魄散，太乙真人尝试以七色宝莲重塑二人肉身，却在过程中遭遇重重挑战。与 2019 年上映的《哪吒之魔童降世》相比，本片在制作层面大幅升级。数据显示，前作镜头数为 1,864 个，其中特效镜头 1,400 个，而《哪吒 2》镜头数量增至 2,427 个，特效镜头更达 1,948 个，超越前作全片总镜头数，视觉效果明显提升。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1292555" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/s_e8baec60662249c495-264x580.jpg" alt="" width="264" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/s_e8baec60662249c495-264x580.jpg 264w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/s_e8baec60662249c495.jpg 409w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 264px" /></p><p>《哪吒 2》不仅在中国市场表现出众，于全球市场亦取得突破。不少在海外影迷赞扬其技术水准已达国际级，与美国、日本动画巨头作品相提并论。但另一方面，也有人质疑票房数据是否经过包装，甚至认为影片票房主要依靠中国市场内部支持，才推升至如此高峰。社交媒体上，支持与反对声音引发激烈讨论，然而票房表现已成事实，无可否认。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1292556" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250218215709-532x580.jpg" alt="" width="532" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250218215709-532x580.jpg 532w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250218215709.jpg 599w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 532px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">资料截至 2025 年 2 月 18 日</p><p>《哪吒 2》的全球票房佳绩也引起国际媒体关注。部分外媒对该片成功感到惊讶，认为动画电影市场竞争激烈，能够突破迪士尼、皮克斯等美国动画巨头作品实属难得。然而，业界普遍认为，下一部有望挑战票房冠军的动画电影将是 2026 年 4 月上映的《超级玛利欧兄弟电影版 2》。</p><p>来源: <a href="https://www.cna.com.tw/news/acn/202502180281.aspx">cna</a></p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
            <wfw:commentRss>https://unwire.hk/2025/02/19/nazha-no1-animation/fun-tech/feed/</wfw:commentRss>
            <slash:comments>0</slash:comments>
        </item>
        <item>
            <title>Dreame V18S Aqua 5 合 1  吸尘洗地器优惠码 + unwire 读者入 CODE 换赠品</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/02/18/dreame-v18s-aqua/shop_guide/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=dreame-v18s-aqua</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/02/18/dreame-v18s-aqua/shop_guide/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Tue, 18 Feb 2025 13:34:58 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[买物情报]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Dreame]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Dreame V18S Aqua]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1292490</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>想轻松吸尘、拖地，重可以除螨、显尘？你可以试用早前我们介绍过的全新 Dreame V18S Aqua 五合一全方位旗舰级吸尘器，一次过满足你 5 个愿望。Unwire.hk 读者只要输入我们的折扣码「DreameUnwire」 ，就可以领取限量礼品包赠品： 1L 清洁液 + 洗地滚刷（总值 HKD 368）。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1292544 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dreamehkv18saqua01mj-398x580.jpg" alt="" width="398" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dreamehkv18saqua01mj-398x580.jpg 398w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dreamehkv18saqua01mj.jpg 408w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 398px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="wp-image-1292545 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/vlcsnap2025021821h30-694x538.jpg" alt="" width="744" height="577" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/vlcsnap2025021821h30-694x538.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/vlcsnap2025021821h30.jpg 1025w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 744px" /></p><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_68550"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/cnGj3ItVrwg?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="fullscreen; accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><h2>Step 1 前往官方网站</h2><p>首先前往 Dreame 官方网站，将 V18s Aqua 加入购物车。</p><p>网站连结：<a href="https://www.dreametech.com.hk/products/v18s-aqua">https://www.dreametech.com.hk/products/v18s-aqua</a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1292491" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/b1-687x580.jpg" alt="" width="687" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/b1-687x580.jpg 687w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/b1.jpg 1065w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 687px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲将 V18s Aqua 加入购物车</p><h2>Step 2 搜寻 V18S 清洁套装 (赠品)</h2><p>点击这个连结：<a href="https://www.dreametech.com.hk/products/%E8%BF%BD%E8%A6%93-dreame-h14-pro-%E6%B8%85%E6%BD%94%E5%A5%97%E8%A3%9D-%E8%B4%88%E5%93%81-%E5%A4%8D%E5%88%B6">连结</a></p><p>或者点击放大镜开启搜寻栏，输入「V18S 清洁套装 (赠品)」。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1292493" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/b4-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/b4-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/b4.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲点击放大镜</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1292495" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/b5-694x457.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="457" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/b5-694x457.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/b5.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲输入「V18S 清洁套装 (赠品)」后再点击箭嘴指住的放大镜</p><p>浏览器会跳页至下面画面，点击绿框购物袋即可加入至购物车。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1292499" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/b9-664x580.jpg" alt="" width="664" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/b9-664x580.jpg 664w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/b9.jpg 1031w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 664px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲点击购物袋将「V18S 清洁套装 (赠品)」加入至购物车</p><h2>Step 3 开启购物车、输入优惠码并结账</h2><p>现在请开启你的购物车，确认吸尘器以及「V18S Aqua 清洁套装」都已经加入购物车，点击结帐。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1292500" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/b11-694x492.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="492" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/b11-694x492.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/b11.jpg 822w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲点击「结帐」</p><p>看见下图结帐画面，请点击「订单摘要」，然后在「礼品卡」栏目输入优惠码「DreameUnwire」，点击套用即可获得赠品：1L 清洁液和洗地滚刷（总值 HKD368），之后按照指示填写个人资料付款即可。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1292502" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/b12-694x388.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="388" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/b12-694x388.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/b12.jpg 825w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲点击「订单摘要」</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1292541" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/2025021892416-694x554.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="554" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/2025021892416-694x554.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/2025021892416.jpg 1127w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲在礼品卡位置输入优惠码「DreameUnwire」</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1292542" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/2025021892426-638x580.jpg" alt="" width="638" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/2025021892426-638x580.jpg 638w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/2025021892426.jpg 990w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 638px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲经套用后，有关赠品便会变成免费</p><p>购买网址: <a href="https://hktvmallredirect.com/W27gpFAt">https://hktvmallredirect.com/W27gpFAt</a></p><br /><b>
]]>
