            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>DJI Osmo Mobile 手机稳定器已来到第 7 代了，今代又有什么改进呢？不过小编更感兴趣的是刚收到的 DJI Phantom 4 积木呢！</p><p><a title="_DSC7210" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/202198613@N06/54335400886/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54335400886_7621542aa4_h.jpg" alt="_DSC7210" width="1600" height="1067" /></a></p><p>早前 DJI 官网发出的产品预告宣传图，正是 DJI Osmo Mobile 新增的多功能追踪模块，即外置 Tracker，亦是第 7 代的卖点，其实其他的功能都与上代差不多，稳定器的外观设计也是差不多；而另外有分别的就是第７代会分为两个版本，Osmo Mobile 7P 及 Osmo Mobile 7，主要分别如下：</p><p>Osmo Mobile 7P：黑色为主色，附有多功能追踪模块，内建延长杆可伸展延长。<br />
Osmo Mobile 7：灰色为主色，没有多功能追踪模块，需另购；稳定器不可伸展延长。</p><p><a title="_DSC7171" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/202198613@N06/54335400696/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54335400696_72cb783e22_h.jpg" alt="_DSC7171" width="1600" height="1067" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">Osmo Mobile 7P 与 Osmo Mobile 7 的包装盒</p><p><a title="_DSC7204" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/202198613@N06/54335631443/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54335631443_918ca61438_h.jpg" alt="_DSC7204" width="1600" height="1067" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">Osmo Mobile 7P 明显较长</p><p style="text-align: center;"><a title="_DSC7205" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/202198613@N06/54335631418/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54335631418_f693bdf929_h.jpg" alt="_DSC7205" width="1600" height="1067" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;"><a title="_DSC7206" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/202198613@N06/54335400881/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54335400881_f9a983402f_h.jpg" alt="_DSC7206" width="1600" height="1067" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">Osmo Mobile 7P 附有多功能追踪模块</p><p><a title="_DSC7177" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/202198613@N06/54335631238/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54335631238_8702cc4424_h.jpg" alt="_DSC7177" width="1600" height="1067" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">Osmo Mobile 7P</p><p><a title="_DSC7193" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/202198613@N06/54335631123/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54335631123_c8739fb434_h.jpg" alt="_DSC7193" width="1600" height="1067" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">7P 内建延长杆</p><h2>多功能追踪模块 Tracker 主要功能</h2><p>基本上现世代的手机拍片都已非常稳定，再加上用了稳定器后，画面稳定情况大家都已经知道，而 DJI 云台增稳效果一向也不错，这方面也不用特别多说，反而是这个多功能追踪模块又有何乾坤？现在讲讲它的主要功能。</p><p><a title="_DSC7180" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/202198613@N06/54335620759/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54335620759_94d3e2b261_h.jpg" alt="_DSC7180" width="1600" height="1067" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">正面设有补光灯及镜头</p><p><a title="_DSC7181" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/202198613@N06/54334495677/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54334495677_7804c54b37_h.jpg" alt="_DSC7181" width="1600" height="1067" /></a></p><p><a title="_DSC7182" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/202198613@N06/54335818915/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54335818915_54df178f5f_h.jpg" alt="_DSC7182" width="1600" height="1067" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">补光灯，以及开关键</p><p><a title="_DSC7183" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/202198613@N06/54334495657/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54334495657_c71fa65fe4_h.jpg" alt="_DSC7183" width="1600" height="1067" /></a></p><p><a title="_DSC7184" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/202198613@N06/54335631168/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54335631168_b857f7e74c_h.jpg" alt="_DSC7184" width="1600" height="1067" /></a></p><p><a title="_DSC7203" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/202198613@N06/54335620989/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54335620989_56f67e79b4_h.jpg" alt="_DSC7203" width="1600" height="1067" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><strong>1. 智能跟拍</strong><br />
手机连上追踪模块后，可以立即采用手机的相机 App 便可使用 Tracker 追踪，或者用 Mimo App 也可。亦可搭配直播软件、视频会议软件及语音通话时使用智能跟随。多功能追踪模组可前后切换，支援前后镜头的跟拍。</p><div style="padding: 46.15% 0 0 0; position: relative;"><iframe style="position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;" title="ScreenRecording_02-18-2025 14-24-38_1" src="https://player.vimeo.com/video/1057840024?badge=0&amp;autopause=0&amp;player_id=0&amp;app_id=58479" frameborder="0"></iframe></div><p>&nbsp;<br />
&nbsp;</p><div></div><div></div><div><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1292540" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/1d080f119b074d388399-694x556.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="556" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/1d080f119b074d388399-694x556.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/1d080f119b074d388399.jpg 1124w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></div><p style="text-align: center;">Tracker 的各项设定</p><p><strong>2. 色温与亮度补光</strong><br />
提供四档色温与四档亮度调节，这方面对于自拍的用家最为用得著；而 OM7P 可透过侧面波轮控制补光灯，滑动波轮调节亮度或色温。</p><p><a title="_DSC7198" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/202198613@N06/54335631038/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54335631038_9fe9f3db75_h.jpg" alt="_DSC7198" width="1600" height="1067" /></a></p><p><a title="_DSC7202" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/202198613@N06/54334495917/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54334495917_95bcc8b18d_h.jpg" alt="_DSC7202" width="1600" height="1067" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">滑动波轮调节亮度</p><p><strong>3. 收音功能</strong><br />
可与 DJI Mic Mini 发射器连上收音，提升影片的收音质素。</p><p><a title="_DSC6179" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/202198613@N06/54335819040/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54335819040_0bf452be02_h.jpg" alt="_DSC6179" width="1600" height="900" /></a></p><p><a title="_DSC7173" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/202198613@N06/54334495672/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54334495672_2ce7572446_h.jpg" alt="_DSC7173" width="1600" height="1067" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">Tracker 亦可单独购买</p><h2>OM7 定价抵玩</h2><p>而稳定器方面，OM7P 与 OM7 升级了云台结构，展开云台只需一步，按下关机键后，云台会自动回到可折叠的位置，一步即可折叠，适合新手快速使用。另外今代续航力亦非常强，可以使用 10 小时，绝对足够一天的拍摄。另外值得留意的是，OM7P 售价为 HK$979，而 OM7 则是 HK$599，今代 OM7 的定价又几抵玩啊～</p><p><a title="_DSC7192" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/202198613@N06/54335631128/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54335631128_5566d19ca4_h.jpg" alt="_DSC7192" width="1067" height="1600" /></a></p><p>售价：<br />
DJI OM7P：HK$979<br />
DJI OM7：HK$599<br />
DJI OM7 Tracker：HK$329</p><h2>同场加映：Phantom 4 Pro V2.0 积木</h2><p>小编收到 DJI 送出的贺年套装，内有其中一样最为值得与读者分享的，就是这套 Phantom 4 Pro V2.0 积木，还记得当年小编第一次买的航拍机，就是 Phantom 2，当时是没有图传也没有云台，要另购安装上机身，而镜头则是用上了 GoPro 3，当年出外航拍时是要放入小型的行李喼中，所以小编对于 Phantom 的机种，特别有感觉的。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1292530" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/d295cc0225224e278d2a-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/d295cc0225224e278d2a-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/d295cc0225224e278d2a-scaled.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1292531" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/e448c88c65634155a02d-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/e448c88c65634155a02d-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/e448c88c65634155a02d-scaled.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1292532" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/ceccc5b8cce94a15b53e-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/ceccc5b8cce94a15b53e-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/ceccc5b8cce94a15b53e-scaled.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>本以为这套 Phantom 4 Pro V2.0 积木，很快便可以砌好，原来设计都很讲究，积木采用 1:1.6 的比例，总数有 817 块，除了还原了 Phantom 4 Pro V2.0 的外型外，另一半是采用了透明壳的设计，让你透视到内部的机件架构，所以透视那边的就有更多的积木要砌了；另外航拍机的另一个象征就是其四个螺旋桨，内建有齿轮结构，你只要转动其中一只桨，就会连动另外三只螺旋桨一起转动。小编完成它需时大约 5 小时，另外要注意的是内部的机件架构有些位置较为复杂，小型零件也较多，小心砌错位。</p><p><a title="_DSC7155" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/202198613@N06/54334495737/in/d